name: As a user I can login with a valid credentials

testSteps.description: 1: As a user I can login with a valid credentials ({email=someoneme1@mail.com, password=123123, fullname=Firstname Lastname})

children.description: Given I set API endpoint valid for register user
When I enter a valid email
And I enter a valid password
And I enter a valid fullname
And I send request to login user "someoneme1@mail.com" and "123123" and "Firstname Lastname"
Then I received status code 200 OK login user
And I received token login user data response
